    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Committee shall consist of members selected by the national library associations (…) The duties of the Committee shall be to select the time and place for international library conferences and, with the co-operation of local committees, to prepare programs for such conferences; and to make investigations and recommendations concerning international relations between libraries, organizations of librarians and bibliographers, and other agencies."@en;
