    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Language Equality Network (ELEN) is a non-governmental organisation. ELEN has as its goal the promotion and protection of European lesser-used (i.e. regional, minority, endangered, indigenous, co-official and smaller national) languages, to work towards linguistic equality for these languages, and multilingualism, under the broader framework of human rights."@en;
