    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "CoCom was an international committee established by Western bloc powers during the Cold War, to put an arms embargo on COMECON countries."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COCOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COCOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001024"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
