<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2ba38096f25b2e2b1dc8a36438c1b67c>.
<#2ba38096f25b2e2b1dc8a36438c1b67c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/TUTB>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:07.924Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#2ba38096f25b2e2b1dc8a36438c1b67c> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/TUTB> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "true";
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> true;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "European Trade Union Technical Bureau for Health and Safety"@en, "Technický úrad Európskeho odborového zväzu pre bezpečnosť a ochranu zdravia"@sk, "Euroopa Töötervishoiu ja Tööohutuse Ametiühingute tehniline büroo"@et, "Europees Technisch Vakbondsbureau voor gezondheid en veiligheid"@nl, "Bureau technique syndical européen pour la santé et la sécurité"@fr, "Oficina Técnica Sindical Europea para la Salud y la Seguridad"@es, "Eiropas Arodbiedrību veselības un drošības tehniskais birojs"@lv, "Euroopan ammattiyhdistyksen terveys- ja turvallisuusasioiden tekninen toimisto"@fi, "Uffiċċju Tekniku tat-Trade Union Ewropew għas-Saħħa u s-Sigurtà"@mt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Le Bureau Technique Syndical Européen pour la Santé et la Sécurité a été créé à l’initiative de la Confédération Européenne des Syndicats pour promouvoir un haut niveau de santé et de sécurité sur les lieux de travail en Europe. Le BTS a assuré un suivi de l’élaboration, de la transposition et de la mise en oeuvre des législations européennes dans le domaine de la santé et de la sécurité au travail. Il a animé des réseaux d’experts en matière de normalisation technique et de substances dangereuses. Le BTS est un membre associé du Comité Européen de Normalisation. Le BTS a coopèree avec les deux autres instituts de la CES, avec l’Institut syndical européen – ISE dans le domaine des relations sociales et avec l’Académie syndicale européenne – ASE en matière de formation."@fr, "The European Trade Union Technical Bureau for Health and Safety (TUTB) was founded by the European Trade Union Confederation to promote high standards of health and safety in European workplaces. The TUTB monitored the framing, national incorporation and implementation of European legislation in the field of occupational health and safety. The TUTB provided resources of expertise to trade union members of the Advisory Committee on Safety, Hygiene and Health Protection at Work, which met in Luxembourg, and the Bilbao-based European Agency for Safety and Health at Work. The TUTB worked in co-operation with the other ETUC institutes, with the ETUI – European Trade Union Institute in the field of industrial relations and with ETUCO – European Trade Union College in the field of education and training."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "TUTB"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001289"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "TUTB"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "TUTB"@en, "BTS"@fr, "TGB"@de;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/TUTB_1989_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "TUTB";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "TUTB";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "TUTB";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1989-01-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "TUTB";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/end.use> "2005-03-31"
}
<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#965cd51d7eab442bfe3bebdb5d6c075b>.
<#965cd51d7eab442bfe3bebdb5d6c075b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_ECHR>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:07.929Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#965cd51d7eab442bfe3bebdb5d6c075b> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_ECHR> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "true";
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#deprecated> true;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Ευρωπαϊκή Επιτροπή ανθρωπίνων δικαιωμάτων"@el, "Euroopa Inimõiguste Komisjon"@et, "Comisia Europeană a Drepturilor Omului"@ro, "Evropska komisija za človekove pravice"@sl, "Kummissjoni Ewropea għad-Drittijiet tal-Bniedem"@mt, "An Coimisiún Eorpach um Chearta an Duine"@ga, "Európska komisia pre ľudské práva"@sk, "Commissione europea dei diritti dell’uomo"@it, "Comissão Europeia dos Direitos Humanos"@pt, "Europäische Kommission für Menschenrechte"@de, "Eiropas Cilvēktiesību komisija"@lv, "Europos žmogaus teisių komisija"@lt, "Den Europæiske Menneskerettighedskommission"@da, "Comisión Europea de Derechos Humanos"@es, "Europeiska kommissionen för de mänskliga rättigheterna"@sv, "Европейска комисия по правата на човека"@bg, "Emberi Jogok Európai Bizottsága"@hu, "Commission européenne des droits de l’homme"@fr, "Europejska Komisja Praw Człowieka"@pl, "Europska komisija za ljudska prava"@hr, "European Commission of Human Rights"@en, "Evropská komise pro lidská práva"@cs, "Euroopan ihmisoikeustoimikunta"@fi, "Europese Commissie voor de Rechten van de Mens"@nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "European Commission of Human Rights was a special body of the Council of Europe. Individuals did not have direct access to the European Court of Human Rights; they had to apply to this commission which – if found the case to be well-founded – launched a case in the Court on the individual’s behalf. Protocol 11 of the European Convention on Human Rights which came into force in 1998 abolished the commission, enlarged the Court, and allowed individuals to take cases directly to it."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COB0001654"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "COU_EUR_ECHR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COU_EUR_ECHR"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COU_EUR_ECHR_1953_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "COU_EUR_ECHR";
