    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "European Stability Initiative (ESI) is a think tank for South East Europe and EU enlargement. It films and reports on the Balkans, Turkey, Central Europe and the South Caucasus. ESI is committed to provide policy makers with relevant strategic analysis."@en;
