    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Južni Pacifik"@hr, "Tichomořské společenství"@cs, "Communauté du Pacifique"@fr, "Wspólnota Pacyfiku"@pl, "Stillehavsfællesskabet"@da, "Pacific Community"@en, "Pacific community"@sv, "Komunità tal-Paċifiku"@mt, "Comunitatea Pacificului"@ro, "Comunidad del Pacífico"@es, "Pazifik-Gemeinschaft"@de, "Klusā okeāna Kopiena"@lv, "Тихоокеанската общност"@bg, "Vaikse ookeani ühendus"@et, "Tyynenmeren yhteisö"@fi, "Pacifiške skupnost"@sl, "Csendes-óceáni Közösség"@hu, "Pacifische Gemeenschap"@nl, "Ramiojo vandenyno bendrija"@lt, "Comunità del Pacifico"@it, "Κοινότητα του Ειρηνικού"@el, "Comunidade do Pacífico"@pt, "Tichomorského spoločenstva"@sk, "Pobal an Aigéin Chiúin"@ga;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Pacific Community is a regional intergovernmental organisation whose membership includes both nations and territories in the Pacific Ocean and their metropolitan powers. It aims to \"develop the technical, professional, scientific, research, planning and management capability of Pacific Island people and directly provide information and advice, to enable them to make informed decisions about their future development and well-being.\""@en;
